# Invitation to Qualify for Construction Services to Build the Lake Superior Discovery Centre

## Solicitation Information
* **Reference Number**: WS3817235738-Doc3904908165
* **Solicitation Number**: WS3817235738
* **Publication Date**: March 14, 2023
* **Closing Date**: April 18, 2023 (1:00 PM, EDT)
* **Procurement Category**: Construction Services, cnst
* **Regions of Delivery**: Ontario (except National Capital Region)

## Project Overview
The Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC) invites qualified contractors to submit an expression of interest for the construction services needed for Phase 1 of the Lake Superior Discovery Centre project in Ontario.

## Criteria for the Tender
The selection of the successful contractor will be based on a combined rating of technical merit and price.

## Associated Trade Agreements
Bids from contractors eligible under various international and regional trade agreements, including the World Trade Organization Agreement on Government Procurement (WTO GPA), are also welcome.

## Contact Information
For any questions or clarifications regarding this invitation, interested contractors can contact Zobia Essa at the PSPC, who can be reached by email at [zobia.essa@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca](mailto:zobia.essa@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca).

## Bid Documents and Information

* Tenders must be submitted electronically to the PSPC.
* The bid solicitation number and name of the contractor must be identified in the subject line of the email.
* Please refer to the bid solicitation documents for submission requirements.

## Queries or Clarifications
Questions or queries should be directed to Zobia Essa at [zobia.essa@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca](mailto:zobia.essa@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca) by the closing date and time indicated below. Late responses will not be accepted.

### Closing Date and Time: April 18, 2023 (1:00 PM, EDT)
Late responses may be declared non-responsive.

## Appendices

This bid solicitation cancels and supersedes the previous solicitation. All submissions must be received by the PSPC on or before the specified closing date and time. Any submissions received after this date may be declared non-responsive. Please contact Zobia Essa for any questions regarding the submission requirements.
